version_description: As with my other bass tabs, this is written in a linear fashion to try to convey a sense of rhythm. One dash equals one eighth note. Guitar chords and lyrics included.

performance.name: Live version from "Before the Frost...Until the Freeze"
performance.comment: It was recorded before a live audience at Levon Helm's Woodstock, NY studio, The Barn in late February and early March, 2009.

version_description: For standard tuning, no capo, and in key with the original.
